		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />It looks really amazing, great job. <br /><br />I would say the bright reflection on the tubes is what may cause confusion about what is at the front and at the back. Maybe the brightest color should be exclusive to things at the front, so making the reflections one tone darker could help with clarity.<br /><br />edit: but on your tube screenshot it doesn't get as confusing because the orange stuff pops out more. Very good overall!

		

