	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Re: Critique this screen/these graphics</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />0D causes distortion on some TVs because it's actually a lower signal level than black is supposed to be. Use 0F (or anything xE or xF) instead for maximum compatibility.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


